3D GEOMETRY RELATIONS
  inner prod:   u'.v = |u|.|v| cos(u^v)
  cross prod:   uxv = |u|.|v| sin(u^v) \vec{n}
  mixed prod:   (uxv)'.w = u'.(vxw) = det(u,v,w)
  outer prod:   u.v' = matrix
